Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再坚持一下…镜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马先生
