Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早就跑这里来 真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这块石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都带著它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 多亏得到了它 我才被救赎了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的十分感谢
